Description: Werner-style UI for FSM.
  Click for brighter, hold for dimmer, tail switch for on/off.
  Plus config/utility modes on "hold side-switch while turning on".
Authors: ToyKeeper
MCU: attiny85
Button-Type: momentary + clicky
Memory: yes
Modes: discrete ramp, battcheck, tempcheck, config, momentary
Extras: thermal regulation, LVP, dual PWM, triple PWM

